      "concern": "Unconstrained self-organization often leads to chaotic, pathological, or highly inefficient emergent behaviors. There's no inherent guarantee that 'adaptation' will converge towards robust reasoning or general intelligence rather than local optima, instability, or even system collapse. The idea lacks any guiding principles or constraints for this self-organization."
